item.title: CVE-2024-5318|2024-05-24T12:44:25.720Z -- GitLab -- GitLab
item.description: An issue has been discovered in GitLab CE/EE affecting all versions starting from 11.11 prior to 16.10.6, starting from 16.11 prior to 16.11.3, and starting from 17.0 prior to 17.0.1. A Guest user can view dependency lists of private projects through job artifacts.
